description:
As tension builds in the Indo-Pacific region and around the world, the United States military is training Army soldiers, Navy sailors, Marines, and Air Force airmen to be ready for war. But there's more to the military than combat. Fueling these future warfighters are culinary specialists tasked with preparing, cooking, and serving thousands of meals a day. In 2024, "Boot Camp" went inside US military training programs and colleges to find out what it takes to join the ranks of those willing to protect and serve their country.
